        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2558234376" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16820943890058742156">The conclusion to this epic series. Not as groundbreaking as other volumes, but still a worthy ending and a powerful message that seems today more relevant than ever.<br/>Will be coming back to this series.</span>

          </span>
